currency to the region to be exchanged for old bills. The Contra
statement said the rebels recovered 10 million new cordobas in the
crash.
   The Contras say they downed 26 helicopters with Redeye missiles
last year. Foreign military observers put the number at a dozen.
The Sandinistas admitted to six.
