   Tom Selleck and two top executives from his
``Magnum P.I.'' television series are considering producing another
series in Hawaii that could make its debut this fall.
   Selleck, along with ``Magnum'' co-executive producer Charles
Floyd Johnson and head writer Chris Abbott formed their own
