<TEXT>
   Tony Curtis, Zsa Zsa Gabor and Cesar
Romero were among the more than 2,000 well-heeled revelers who
celebrated the Hotel del Coronado's 100th anniversary in grand
style.
   ``It's fantastic. You don't see too many parties like this any
more,'' Romero said of the Friday night fund-raising bash that
recaptured highlights of the seaside resort's history.
